CSS class:

In css box model we can use class for separating the even ones actually.
 Next we can add multiple classes together by adding them with a space.
[eg:<h1 class="title" "title2 title3"] easy nd simple

CSS BOX MODEL:
   *Border
   *padding
   *margin

->Border
   *thickness,
   *style[Solid,dotted,dashed,groove]
->padding
    *it is used for making the text align in center within the border.
->margin
    *it is used for making space outside the border.

    CHOOSING COLORS:
        #color hunt web is used for getimg perfect colors